  </div>
  
  <div class="rightFloatvideo1">
  <tab/><video src="../media/Unit02_e1g.flv" mode="16" id="1009" autoPlay="false" width="320" height="240" /><tab/><tab/>
  <video src="../media/Unit02_e1h.flv" mode="16" id="1010" autoPlay="false" width="320" height="240" />
  </div>
  
  <br/><br/>
  <div class="brieftext">
  <p>3.<tab/>Do you work or do you study? I study engineering / I'm a teacher, etc. Follow with a brief description.<br/>
  After this giving of personal information, you will be asked to give your opinion on general topics, such as friends, family, leisure activities, celebrations, or hobbies.</p>
  </div>
